- `DEVICE_SYNC_WORKERS`
- `DEVICE_SYNC_QUEUE_MAXSIZE`
- `OUTBOX_POLL_INTERVAL_SEC`
- `OUTBOX_BATCH_SIZE`
- `OUTBOX_MAX_RETRIES`
- `RECONCILIATION_INTERVAL_SEC`
- `RECONCILIATION_DRIFT_WARN_MINUTES`
